@startuml
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype ortho

title AIPOT System Architecture (Code-Aligned)

actor "Player" as Player
actor "PRO Player" as Pro

node "Web Client" {
  component "Frontend\n(Vite + React + React Router)" as FE
  component "Session Layer\n(localStorage JWT + user profile)" as Session
  FE --> Session
}

node "Backend API (NestJS)" {
  component "AuthModule\n/auth/*" as AuthM
  component "LobbyModule\n/lobby/*" as LobbyM
  component "RoomsModule\n/rooms/*" as RoomsM
  component "GameModule\n/game/*" as GameM
  component "HandReviewModule\n/hand-review/*" as ReviewM
  component "AiModule\n/ai/*" as AiM
  component "ProfileModule\n/profile/*" as ProfileM
  component "SocialModule\n/social/*" as SocialM

  component "UsersService" as UsersSvc
  component "StoreService\n- room/game state engine\n- social graph\n- hand review persistence\n- timeout/runout rules" as StoreSvc
}

database "MySQL\n(TypeORM)\nstate_snapshots" as MySQL

cloud "LLM Providers" {
  component "OpenAI" as OpenAI
  component "Claude" as Claude
  component "Gemini" as Gemini
  component "Local LLM Gateway\n(OpenAI-compatible)" as LocalLLM
}

Player --> FE : sign-in / quick-play / table-play
Pro --> FE : premium hand review / paid model use

FE --> AuthM : auth APIs
FE --> LobbyM : table list / quick-play / leaderboard
FE --> RoomsM : create/join/seat/bot/blind management
FE --> GameM : state sync / act / timer-sync / next-hand
FE --> ReviewM : hand list/detail + analyze status polling
FE --> ProfileM : profile/stats/avatar/store
FE --> SocialM : friends / requests / room invites

AuthM --> UsersSvc
ProfileM --> UsersSvc

UsersSvc --> StoreSvc
LobbyM --> StoreSvc
RoomsM --> StoreSvc
GameM --> StoreSvc
ReviewM --> StoreSvc
SocialM --> StoreSvc

GameM --> AiM : bot decision
ReviewM --> AiM : hand analysis

AiM --> OpenAI
AiM --> Claude
AiM --> Gemini
AiM --> LocalLLM

StoreSvc --> MySQL : hydrate/persist snapshot

note right of GameM
- getState/act/timerSync 시 BOT 턴 즉시 처리
- 액션 타이머 만료 자동 처리(fold/check)
- all-in runout/스트리트 전환/승자 계산 관리
end note

note right of ReviewM
- 전체 액션 분석은 비동기 큐 방식
- 상태: pending/running/completed/failed
- 결과는 HandReviewRecord.analyses[]에 저장
end note

@enduml
